# Greenhouse Effect Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Sun] --> B[Shortwave Radiation Reaches Earth]
    B --> C[Earth's Surface Absorbs and Heats Up]
    C --> D[Earth Emits Longwave Infrared Radiation]
    D --> E[Greenhouse Gases Absorb Infrared Radiation]
    E --> F[Greenhouse Gases Re-radiate Heat in All Directions]
    F --> G[Heat Trapped in Atmosphere]
    G --> H[Earth's Temperature Increases]
    F --> I[Heat Escapes to Space]

